graph TB

  subgraph Axes[Time axes]
    ET[Event time]
    VT[Valid time]
    TT[Transaction time]
  end

  subgraph Objects[KFM domain objects]
    Obs[Observation or event]
    State[Feature state or statement]
    Artifact[Artifact]
    Run[Run receipt]
    Bundle[Evidence bundle]
    Story[Story node version]
  end

  Obs --> ET
  State --> VT
  Artifact --> TT
  Run --> TT
  Bundle --> TT
  Story --> TT

  Obs -->|captured_as| Artifact
  State -->|represented_in| Artifact
  Run -->|produces| Artifact
  Artifact -->|resolves_to| Bundle
  Story -->|cites| Bundle

  subgraph TruthPath[Truth path zones]
    RAW[RAW] --> WORK[WORK or Quarantine] --> PROCESSED[PROCESSED] --> CATALOG[CATALOG] --> PUBLISHED[PUBLISHED]
  end

  RAW -->|acquired_at| TT
  PROCESSED -->|promoted_at| TT
  PUBLISHED -->|served_as_of| TT
  CATALOG -->|cross_links| Bundle

  subgraph Queries[Common query modes]
    QEvent[Filter by event-time window]
    QValid[Query by valid-time interval]
    QAsOf[Reproduce: as-of transaction time]
  end

  QEvent --> ET
  QValid --> VT
  QAsOf --> TT

  subgraph Guidance[Recommended default]
    Default[Default: Event time + Transaction time]
    Optional[Add Valid time for administrative truth changes]
  end

  Default --> ET
  Default --> TT
  Optional --> VT
